    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to TicketingSystem! Your privacy is very important to us. This privacy policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and the steps we take to protect your data.</p>

    <p>By using our services, you agree to the terms outlined in this privacy policy.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Personal Information</strong>: When you purchase a ticket or create an account, we may collect your name, email address, phone number, and payment details. This information is essential for providing you with our services.</li>
        <li><strong>Non-Personal Information</strong>: We collect certain information automatically, such as IP addresses, browser types, and the pages you visit on our website. This helps us improve your experience and the overall functionality of our site.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies</strong>: Our website uses cookies to personalize your browsing experience. Cookies help us understand your preferences and provide customized services. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, although some features may not work properly.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Provide Services</strong>: We use your personal information to process ticket purchases, deliver tickets, and manage your bookings.</li>
        <li><strong>Improve User Experience</strong>: The data we collect helps us improve our website, tailor our services to your needs, and provide a personalized experience.</li>
        <li><strong>Marketing Communications</strong>: We may use your contact information to send you updates about new events or promotions. You can opt-out at any time by clicking the "unsubscribe" link in our emails.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties. However, we may share your data with trusted service providers who help us operate our platform, such as payment processors. These parties are obligated to keep your information confidential and secure.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We are committed to protecting your information. We use a combination of encryption, firewalls, and secure access protocols to safeguard your data. While we strive to ensure the security of your personal information, please note that no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time. If you wish to make changes to your account or have any concerns about your data, please contact us at [support@ticketingsystem.com].</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We encourage you to review this policy occasionally to stay informed of any updates.</p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please reach out to us at <strong>[support@ticketingsystem.com].</strong> We are here to help.</p>

    <p>Thank you for trusting TicketingSystem with your information!</p>
